Hey all. *ducks as eggs and other various veggies fly by*

Ya, ya, I know. =p

Anyway, I've stopped for a short time (namely one post) to announce 
some stuff. First thing, Rudrak is now the owner of the rpg. It 
needed to be done since me staying the owner right now is rather 
silly. I just don't have any time set aside for role playing right 
now, so -- if it wasn't obvious already -- I'm taking a break. I'm 
not gunna say that I'm gunna be back on a specific day, but I do 
think that I will return eventually.

I guess that Noir will have to be under cardhead's control till the 
end of the battle. And ya, Aerosmith yer gunna be controlling Hydras 
for a while longer, I hope you don't mind. =) As for Switchblade, he 
can stay as an NPC repair bot in the Predacon base if nobody has any 
complaints. Also, should anyone want to use any of my characters 
(this being unlikely since most people are busy with their own 
characters =p) then you can email me anytime at x_rauq_x@....

Rudrak mentioned that elections are gunna happen again (to fill my 
spot probably), and I wish all who aspire to gain more influence 
good luck. =)

Jeff (-rAuq-x)
